{"tid":10080,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"美女把前室友睪丸 當橘子捏爆","createTime":"2016-11-28T20:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T01:24:42.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27bce9a93423f95221505972f4ee6ad41b122315","tid":10080,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20131010/280_8d51400f647a6378d9aba14bb0bf3730.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20131010%2F280_8d51400f647a6378d9aba14bb0bf3730.jpg&h=a5bd3ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【施旖婕╱綜合外電報導】美國南卡羅來納州一名33歲女子辛萊塔瑞(Jennifer Singletary)，在前天醉醺醺地回到前租屋處拿東西時，竟把前室友的睪丸捏爆，最後辛萊塔瑞被扭送警局。<br />\n<br />\n據美國《哈芬登郵報》報導，辛萊塔瑞和36歲男子道奎斯特(Dolquist)原本是室友，最近辛萊塔瑞搬家，前天她回到原租屋處拿東西。但辛萊塔瑞當天有喝醉的狀況，她嫌道奎斯特擋住她的去路，突然出了一拳向道奎斯特揮去，還緊捏道奎斯特的睪丸。<br />\n<br />\n據道奎斯特的說法，睪丸被捏到流血。道奎斯特最後奮力從「魔掌」掙脫並報警，警方也將辛萊塔瑞逮捕。"},{"pid":"cd61554f5b8a18bdfd691a2dd5d1958b3bbef443","tid":10080,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T21:12:12.000Z","msg":"41J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e44e5c0866b9d57725b459fbbaef65c8317cce","tid":10080,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:24:42.000Z","msg":"施旖婕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}